<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <title>Portfolio Creator - Home</title>
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/home.css">
        <script defer src="/javascript/home.js"></script>
      </head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="container">
            <h1>Portfolio Creator</h1>
            <nav>
                <ul class="nav-links">
                    <li><input type="text" placeholder="Search users..." class="search-bar"></li>
                    <li><a href="/signup" class="btn">Sign Up</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/login" class="btn">Login</a></li>
                </ul>
            </nav>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section class="hero">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Build Your Portfolio Effortlessly</h2>
                <p>Showcase your projects, skills, and professional experiences in just a few clicks. Join our platform to create a personalized portfolio tailored just for you!</p>
                <div class="cta-buttons">
                    <a href="/signup" class="btn primary-btn">Get Started</a>
                    <a href="/login" class="btn secondary-btn">Login</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="user-showcase">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Users Who Created Their Portfolios</h2>
                <div class="user-list">
                    <div class="user-card">User 1</div>
                    <div class="user-card">User 2</div>
                    <div class="user-card">User 3</div>
                    <div class="user-card">User 4</div>
                    <div class="user-card">User 5</div>
                    <div class="user-card">User 6</div>
                    <div class="user-card">User 7</div>
                    <div class="user-card">User 8</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="about-company">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>About Us</h2>
                <p>At Portfolio Creator, we believe that everyone deserves a place to showcase their skills and achievements. Our platform simplifies the process of creating professional portfolios, enabling you to highlight your experiences, share your projects, and enhance your digital presence.</p>
                <p>Founded in 2024, we aim to provide a seamless user experience that helps individuals from all walks of life stand out in the competitive digital world. Whether you're a student, professional, or freelancer, our portfolio generator adapts to your needs, allowing you to focus on what matters most: your growth and success.</p>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <div class="container">
            <p>&copy; 2024 Portfolio Creator. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
